comments: Great class, great professor. Take him I recommend it.
Great teacher. Great leader. Great information learned in his class. Thankful to have a great teacher.
Very, very informative and overall, great professor. He requires a lot of group work, but assignments are very easy. If you want an easy A, take his course!

Schademan is the man! He is a totally chill guy and although attendance is pretty much required, class was usually pretty interesting everyday. What\'s also cool is that he feels that letter grades are important, but the knowledge at this point is way more valuable than the letter grade itself. I pretty much batted 1000 all semester.
